channel.title: Can Moparscape change you?
channel.description:
I went from this on moparscape [img]http://s15.postimage.org/yo7l9jubd/cheese.png[/img] To this, but I'm not saying it's great. I'm saying I've made progress. This also isn't my best but I wouldn't know how to show my best. http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,529937.0.html
The picture was when I wanted to make a runescape private server since I've played them so much. I tried downloading so many but I didn't know how because I didn't have winrar. Can Moparscape really change people? Ask yourself that.
